core ideas:
    no null/none/void?
    fast
    simple
    prefer verbose


repo management tool:
    tool dep github:StarrFox/regex -> add my regex library as a dependency
    tool dep remove StarrFox/regex -> remove it

    tool run -> runs the current repo's main
    tool run taskname -> runs a user-defined task within the repo's context

    tool test -> runs the current repo's tests

    tool init package -> makes a new package repo
    tool init bin -> makes a new binary repo